<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Subscription Updated - <%= donorName %>
    </title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f7fa;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            background: #4a6fa5;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .logo {
            height: 60px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .church-name {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 10px 0 5px;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .church-motto {
            font-style: italic;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-top: 0;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .receipt-details {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #4a6fa5;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;
        }

        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            min-width: 120px;
            color: #4a6fa5;
        }

        .thank-you {
            font-size: 18px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        .verse {
            font-style: italic;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            margin: 25px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            border-top: 1px dashed #ddd;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed #ddd;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #a3c4ff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .receipt-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #4a6fa5;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 15px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0;
                border-radius: 0;
            }

            .detail-row {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .detail-label {
                margin-bottom: 5px;
            }
        }

        .changes-list {
            background-color: #e3f2fd;
            border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;
        }

        .change-item {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding-left: 15px;
            border-left: 2px solid #2196f3;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="../../public/logo.png" alt="Church Logo" class="logo">
            <div class="church-name">Ethiopian Full Gospel Believers Church (Silver Spring Local)</div>
            <div class="church-motto">Serving Christ Together</div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h1>Your Recurring Donation Has Been Updated</h1>
            <p>Dear <%= donorName %>,</p>

            <p>We've successfully updated your recurring donation as requested. Here's a summary of the changes:</p>

            <div class="changes-list">
                <% changes.forEach(change=> { %>
                    <div class="change-item">
                        <strong>
                            <%= change.field %>:
                        </strong> Changed from <%= change.oldValue %> to <%= change.newValue %>
                    </div>
                    <% }); %>
            </div>

            <div class="receipt-details">
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Current Amount:</div>
                    <div>
                        <%= currency %>
                            <%= currentAmount.toFixed(2) %>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Next Contribution:</div>
                    <div>
                        <%= nextBillingDate %>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Status:</div>
                    <div>
                        <%= subscriptionStatus %>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p>You can review or make additional changes anytime through our <a
                    href="<%= manageSubscriptionUrl %>">donation portal</a>.</p>

            <div class="verse">
                "Give, and it will be given to you. A good measure, pressed down, shaken together and running over, will
                be poured into your lap."<br>
                - Luke 6:38
            </div>

            <p>With gratitude for your continued support,</p>
            <p>
                <strong>Pastor Fitsum Yab</strong><br>
                Grace Community Church
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <div style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                Ethiopian Full Gospel Believers Church (Silver Spring Local)<br>
                914 Silver Spring Ave, Suite 204 B, Silver Spring, MD 20910, USA
            </div>
            <div>
                <a href="mailto:giving@efgbcssl.org">giving@efgbcssl.org</a> |
                <a href="tel:+12408210361">(240) 821-0361</a> |
                <a href="https://efgbcssl.org">efgbcssl.org</a>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-top: 15px; opacity: 0.8;">
                This receipt may be used for tax purposes. No goods or services were provided in exchange for
                this
                donation.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>